gs  and carpeting  A musty or earthy smell can also be an indication of mold growth  If you suspect that mold is present in you work area  you can request a mold investigation by emailing health safety uic edu with your name  phone number  location  and a picture of the area  jpeg or png Mold Factsheet Mold Factsheet Ergonomics Ergonomics refers to the science of designing the work environment to the person i e  poor posture  overuse of muscles and repetitive motion  can lead to cumulative trauma injuries  also known as musculoskeletal disorders  MSD   Ergonomics Factsheet Ergonomics Factsheet Ergonomic Assessment Request Form Ergonomic Assessment Request Form For issues not listed  please email health safety uic edu with your name  phone number health safety uic edu Web Privacy 